    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every facet of this motorcar\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior\u2014has been meticulously maintained to satisfy the most discerning enthusiast. It offers an unrivaled driving experience, entirely free from signs of wear or mechanical compromise. For the individual seeking a specimen of uncompromising quality and heritage, this offering stands as a definitive acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
